        Multiple Offers on Your Brisbane Property: How Sellers Handle Them
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Receiving more than one offer is a good problem to have, but handling it well requires understanding your legal position and what actually makes one offer stronger than another.
      </p>
